Jialat.SubPage

Interface SubPageController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UnzipSubPageController, ZipSubPageController

    public interface SubPageController
extends javafx.fxml.Initializable
    SubPageController Interface An interface which extends Initializable and implemented by its kind such as the ZipSubPage and UnzipSubPage which are used after the main window to get more information about the execution, e.g. the path where the result of zip/unzip will be located, etc.
